videos.description: Wisconsin's Taiwan Deal runs in a 2-yard score for his first career touchdown.
videos.headline: Badgers RB  Deal punches in 1st career TD

videos.description: BYU RB Squally Canada finds a gap and turns on the jets for a 44-yard run.
videos.headline: BYU's Canada bursts for a 44-yard run

videos.description: Squally Canada gets the handoff and runs it in for a  3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Canada runs in a BYU TD

videos.description: BYU pulls a play out of its bag of tricks to take a 14-7 lead over Wisconsin on a 31-yard touchdown pass.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU takes lead on trick play) 2018/09/15

videos.headline: BYU takes lead on trick play

videos.description: Wisconsin RB Alec Ingold  runs in  a 2-yard touchdown to even it up at 14 with BYU.
videos.headline: Wisconsin RB Ingold drives in 2-yard TD

videos.description: Zayne Anderson picks off Wisconsin QB Alex Hornibrook and returns it for 12 yards.
videos.headline: BYU's  Anderson intercepts Hornibrook

videos.description: BYU RB Squally Canada dives in for a 2-yard touchdown, his second of the day.
videos.headline: Canada runs in his 2nd TD of the day

videos.description: Wisconsin K Rafael Gaglianone misses a tying 42-yard field goal attempt,  securing a 24-21 BYU victory.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's missed FG seals BYU win

videos.description: Wisconsin RB Taiwan Deal takes the handoff and runs it in for a 5-yard touchdown, his second of the game.
videos.headline: Deal punches in 5-yard Wisconsin TD
